{"data": [{"id": "4745377", "title": "MTUM: Right Strategy, Wrong Fund", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1680324844/image_1680324844.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Getting over the hump - 4 balls\" data-id=\"1680324844\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1680324844/image_1680324844.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1680324844/image_1680324844.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1680324844/image_1680324844.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1680324844/image_1680324844.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1680324844/image_1680324844.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1680324844/image_1680324844.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1680324844/image_1680324844.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1680324844/image_1680324844.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">PM Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Momentum strategies have outperformed in 2024 and late 2023. The below chart shows the one-year return of a momentum strategy versus the best of all other strategies.</p> <p></p> <p>However, not all momentum ETFs are created equal. This article looks at</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1680324844