"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/C\" title=\"Citigroup Inc.\">C</a></span>), I noted that I am buying every dip and I still stand by it. I believe that 2025 is a pivotal year for Citi's transformation and when the results</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1471694218/image_1471694218.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745376-citigroup-stock-doubters-become-believers-in-2025", "pub_date": "2024-12-19 20:34:11"}, {"id": "4745371", "title": "Why OCSL Could Surprise Bulls", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/145868159/image_145868159.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"US dollart banknotes\" data-id=\"145868159\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"5136px\" height=\"3424px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/145868159/image_145868159.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/145868159/image_145868159.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/145868159/image_145868159.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/145868159/image_145868159.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/145868159/image_145868159.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/145868159/image_145868159.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/145868159/image_145868159.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/145868159/image_145868159.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Yuji Sakai</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Investment Thesis</h2> <p>My last <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4705298-oaktree-specialty-lending-built-for-stability-success\" title=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4705298-oaktree-specialty-lending-built-for-stability-success\" target=\"_blank\">coverage</a> on Oaktree Specialty Lending Corporation (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/OCSL\" title=\"Oaktree Specialty Lending Corporation\">OCSL</a></span>) (rated \u2018buy\u2019) focused on its risk reduction and diversified portfolio with high debt yields. However, since then, the stock has significantly underperformed the broader market. Despite short-term headwinds, OCSL is well-positioned for future growth. Its</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/145868159/image_145868159.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745371-why-ocsl-could-surprise-bulls", "pub_date": "2024-12-19 20:23:41"}, {"id": "4745368", "title": "The Fed Fumble And The Dollar Wrecking Ball", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/685007313/image_685007313.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Mixed Race man watching wrecking ball swinging at wall\" data-id=\"685007313\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"960px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/685007313/image_685007313.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/685007313/image_685007313.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/685007313/image_685007313.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/685007313/image_685007313.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/68500731